Package com.linecorp.centraldogma.common

Common data types and exceptions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Change<T>
    A modification of an individual Entry.
    Entry<T>
    A file or a directory in a repository.
    Query<T>
    A query on an Entry.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Author
    An author of a Commit.
    Commit
    A set of Changes and its metadata.
    QueryResult<T>
    The result of a Query evaluation.
    Revision
    A revision number of a Commit.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ChangeType
    The type of a Change.
    EntryType
    The type of an Entry.
    Markup
    The markup language of a Commit message.
    QueryType
    The type of a Query.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ChangeFormatException
    An IllegalArgumentException exception that is raised when building a Change or an Entry failed due to invalid data format.
    QueryException
    A RuntimeException that is raised when the syntax validation or the evaluation of a Query has failed.
